            <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Which storytelling arc does the following example represent?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;"From the moment I started my master's program, I had one goal: land a role in AI research. I applied to over 50 positions and got rejected from every single one. I revamped my resume, sought out professors for guidance, and built projects to fill the gaps in my portfolio. Slowly, the callbacks started coming. Eventually, I accepted an offer at a company doing exactly the work I had been chasing for two years."&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</mattext>
          </material>
          <response_lid ident="response1" rcardinality="Single">
            <render_choice>
              <response_label ident="992">
                <material>
                  <mattext texttype="text/plain">The Quest (goal-driven mission)</mattext>
                </material>
              </response_label>
              <response_label ident="8517">
